						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Second fragment of the third face of a broken pillar set up on the bund of the well outside the village.</hi></p>						

						<p>12th-13th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">12th-13th Century A.D.,</hi> seems to register a gift of land and money to god Sōmanātha.</p>						

